{"tid":1056012,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"當年今日TVB首播[四驅兄弟]動畫，帶起四驅車熱","createTime":"2019-03-11T01:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T03:19:56.000Z","uid":35166,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"ba54576358278013dcb25d7f3ddcc0846cca403e","tid":1056012,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T01:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xESUOM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xESUOM.png&h=ba715f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在某fb 版面見到<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1632526533677844/posts/2204647799799045?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1632526533677844%2Fposts%2F2204647799799045%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=cbbe9a69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1632526533677844/posts/2204647799799045?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來22年前既3月11日，tvb開始播 四驅兄弟 ，再加上 co co 既宣傳同四驅兄弟漫畫版 ，係香港再次帶起四驅車熱潮 ，<br />\n<br />\n講返 四驅兄弟 又係一套好動畫 故事令你好想追落去<br />\n<br />\n人物各有特色 ，無記配音組又配得好，咁就22年了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港版主題曲 又係正，d詞填得好好，幾興幸童年<br />\n生活在一個還重視廣東話既時光<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TFwT0aMLHWA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTFwT0aMLHWA&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FAg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=b0461b8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TFwT0aMLHWA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我想求 有邊度可以睇返 粵配版四驅兄弟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a38b837a56558febd118b266b3c3f79a70e0df5","tid":1056012,"uid":59602,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T01:55:59.000Z","msg":"同求，但我要四驅小子<br />\n<br />\n上呀！地平線！！"},{"pid":"33c4dad7a5f05da81a96fab7b957b2f1b15b1d08","tid":1056012,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dis